message.body: Kennedy! Its Maria. i would love to come check out the warehouse ar 3:30! should i just meet you there?
Yea! Meet me at broad and Washington at 3:30.
SE corner
I am still freaking out!!!
OMG me too!!!!!! you are a goddess walking among us earthlings!!!!!!
Haha, with our powers combined we will become SO FUCKING FAMOUS!!!!
I was thinking of stopping by tomorrow quickly just to let him know we'll be coming at 11 on Tuesday with a proposal. Cool?
yeah! rock on
Glad I stopped in, he won't be there on Tuesday. Can we do Wednesday before 2?
...and of course during my brief stop in I got to hear an awesome story of how he still has date night every Wednesday with his wife of fifty years.
yes! weds it is. so that will change tuesdays coffee plan... i will coordinate with becky.
We can still meet tues if you guys want to, just for us to go over details. And I actually need to be done by 12:30 on Wednesday.
stand by.... trying to figure out the best options.....
No probs, thanks for being the point person for this!
(1/2) just emailed u about the possibility of you dropping stuff off monday by yourself. we feel we can postpone mech viewing in the name of greasing the wheels
(2/2) ... read it and lemme know what u think
The package is delivered. He will get back to us Friday at the latest.
Do we still wanna meet tomorrow?
i dont think ee need to, but lets keep in touch this week while we wait!
Yup yup! I also finally heard back from dreaming building so worst case scenario I can meet with him. But I am pretty confidant everything is gonna work out!
hey kennedy, i might have to leave town for a week in a few hours.... have u heard from mr. kulis at all?
